## Description {#details}

A container which contains a string, which it owns, plus a precomputed hash.

We do not null-terminate the string.

Definition at line 72 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/cachedhashstring-h">CachedHashString.h</a>.
